class pynumad.objects.Subobjects.BOM

Bases: object

A simple class to organize the attributes of a Bill of Materials

BOM object properties: 1. Layer # 2. Material ID 3. Component or region name 4. Begin station (m) 5. End station (m) 6. Max width (m) 7. Average width (m) 8. 3D area (m^2) 9. Layer thickness (mm) 10. Computed dry layer weight (g)
